reviewText: Wonderful movies.  Can't get enough of his acting.  The DVDs had nothing wrong with them.  They were shipped properly.  Overall good.
This was a great deal. I got this 2 DVD set for under $4! I would say though that it should be stated that this is a FULL SCREEN set. For under $4 I'm OK with it, but I wanted others to know...
Love it! Perfectly Described as delivered! Would buy again from seller!
Arrived quickly;  my husband had never seen Silence of the Lambs, so ordered it.  Getting Hannibal was a bonus!  Classics!
Came very early happy with this product
Classic movies, needed them to round out the collection. Like that both were bundled together at such a great price.

Wow!!What a movie,I Loved it..Anthony Hopkins hits it home as always. I wanted to add this to my personal collection of my favorites. These two movies in my opinion are his best...I didn't move the entire time. Love these movies...

Fast service and the product came in exactly the condition stated. I'm glad it was only Silence of the Lambs and Hannibal, I don't really care for Red Dragon much even though it would have been a little bonus to complete the set.

Second time I purchased this as I had given it away years ago so this is the second time I watched these and they are still as excellent as they were abo.

Forrest
